    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a consistent daily driver. Mechanically, it remains sound and starts up without issue, though it has reached a point where cosmetic wear and tear are visible both inside and out. The interior shows some signs of use, and the exterior has minor blemishes consistent with its age. It has been regularly serviced to ensure it stays roadworthy and reliable for its next owner.",
