      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unrivaled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance that satisfies the most discerning collector. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been meticulously preserved to ensure a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine asset for the sophisticated driver.",
